{"id": "1506503728377757736", "channel_id": "1506503728377757736", "type": 0, "author_id": "1505953646385565736", "author_name": "lost_in_the_mist", "author_bot": false, "content": "為了避免浪費資源，除了新手抽外只花了35無垢之星（但是不知道為什麼我會有狗狗和奧爾拉🤔）\n\n目前打到4-2卡住了，商店有買羅坦3個殘片，然後為了通關和升級角色花了點體力去打慕間演習\n\n感覺我玩的方向不太對，於是上來問問看，想要長期玩，以這篇巴哈文章為基準https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=78829&snA=978，應該算小課（但是未來打算只買大小月卡就好了）\n\n以下是目前隊伍和資源，我的目標是抽阿拉然後組一隊，在其他討論版看到有人推薦阿拉、哈姆林、奧爾拉、卡茜亞\n\n好迷茫，聽說以後還有叫甚麼融災的東西，然後卡池好多感覺好複雜，有人可以指名方向嗎😭😭😭？", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T03:47:58.331000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1506503729220944015", "filename": "Screenshot_20260520-110350.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2980663, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506503728377757736/1506503729220944015/Screenshot_20260520-110350.png?ex=6a0f292e&is=6a0dd7ae&hm=c2e372cb059165206cd44bc2a0673d3c38dac00fda9772b00443e9f332c5229d&"}, {"id": "1506503729975922748", "filename": "Screenshot_20260520-110430.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2983396, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506503728377757736/1506503729975922748/Screenshot_20260520-110430.png?ex=6a0f292e&is=6a0dd7ae&hm=a9d042f4a959b4db718d68b653f4a74ea5157911ff833df3eb129664031579ba&"}, {"id": "1506503730609127474", "filename": "Screenshot_20260520-110456.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2478344, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506503728377757736/1506503730609127474/Screenshot_20260520-110456.png?ex=6a0f292e&is=6a0dd7ae&hm=de100e19b6abd4a435e8677dd549a8da02d68159e67077c328404c2ec67b5851&"}, {"id": "1506503731208781974", "filename": "Screenshot_20260520-110450.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2327570, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506503728377757736/1506503731208781974/Screenshot_20260520-110450.png?ex=6a0f292f&is=6a0dd7af&hm=c8fda8247e56eddf9798c268ac1f15e60d33f02e500e146a95f5e2a443f6ede2&"}, {"id": "150650373189691